# Lake Shore Church — West Loop
# .cursorrules — read this before every task

## Project overview
Full-stack church ministry platform. Monorepo with Next.js web app and Expo React Native mobile app sharing business logic through shared packages.

## Monorepo structure
```
lsc-platform/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/          ← Next.js 14 App Router (public site + portals)
│   └── mobile/       ← Expo + React Native (iOS + Android)
├── packages/
│   ├── ui/           ← Shared design system
│   │   ├── web/      ← Radix UI + Tailwind components
│   │   ├── native/   ← React Native equivalents
│   │   └── tokens.ts ← Shared design tokens
│   ├── db/           ← Supabase client + all typed queries
│   │   ├── client.ts
│   │   ├── types.ts  ← Auto-generated from Supabase
│   │   └── queries/  ← sermons, prayers, events, members, giving, expenses
│   ├── cms/          ← Sanity client + GROQ queries + schemas
│   │   ├── client.ts
│   │   ├── schemas/
│   │   └── queries/
│   └── config/       ← Shared tailwind, tsconfig, eslint
└── turbo.json
```

